---
import SEO from '../../components/SEO.astro';
import Schema from '../../components/Schema.astro';
import LanguageSwitcher from '../../components/LanguageSwitcher.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="32x32" href="/favicon-32x32.png">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="16x16" href="/favicon-16x16.png">
    <link rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="180x180" href="/apple-touch-icon.png">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bebas+Neue&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <!-- SEO Meta Tags -->
    <SEO
        title="Websites Profissionais - Luís Madeira"
        description="Websites modernos que aparecem no Google e convertem visitantes em clientes. Design limpo, rápido e otimizado para negócios locais."
        locale="pt"
    />

    <!-- Structured Data -->
    <Schema type="Service" />
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Navigation -->
    <nav class="navigation">
        <a href="/pt" class="logo">luís madeira</a>
        <div class="nav-links">
            <a href="/pt/#work">Trabalhos</a>
            <div class="nav-dropdown">
                <button class="nav-dropdown-toggle">
                    Serviços
                    <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                        <path d="M7 10L12 15L17 10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                    </svg>
                </button>
                <div class="nav-dropdown-menu">
                    <a href="/pt/consultoria">Consultoria</a>
                    <a href="/pt/servicos">Websites</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <a href="/pt/sobre">Sobre</a>
            <a href="/pt/#contact">Contacto</a>
            <LanguageSwitcher currentPath="/pt/servicos" />
        </div>
        <div class="mobile-menu-toggle">
            <span></span>
            <span></span>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="page-hero">
        <div class="page-hero-content">
            <h1>WEBSITES PROFISSIONAIS</h1>
            <p class="page-hero-subtitle">Websites modernos que aparecem no Google e convertem visitantes em clientes.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <section class="content-section">
        <div class="content-wrapper">
            <div class="content-main">
                <h2>Para Quem É Isto</h2>
                <p>Se precisa de uma presença online profissional que funcione para o seu negócio, posso ajudar. Crio websites que não são apenas bonitos, mas que aparecem no Google e convertem visitantes em clientes.</p>

                <h2>O Que Ofereço</h2>

                <div class="service-options">
                    <div class="option-card">
                        <h3>Landing Pages</h3>
                        <p>Páginas simples e focadas, ideais para campanhas específicas, promoções ou quando precisa de algo rápido.</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Design limpo e moderno</li>
                            <li>Otimizado para conversões</li>
                            <li>Rápido de carregar</li>
                            <li>Formulário de contacto integrado</li>
                        </ul>
                        <div class="option-timing">
                            <strong>Prazo:</strong> 1-2 semanas
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="option-card featured">
                        <div class="featured-badge">Mais Popular</div>
                        <h3>Websites Completos com SEO</h3>
                        <p>Websites multi-página construídos para rankear no Google e atrair clientes locais através de pesquisa orgânica.</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Design profissional e responsivo</li>
                            <li>Múltiplas páginas otimizadas</li>
                            <li>SEO técnico completo</li>
                            <li>Configuração Google Analytics</li>
                            <li>Conteúdo otimizado para pesquisa local</li>
                            <li>Schema markup implementado</li>
                        </ul>
                        <div class="option-timing">
                            <strong>Prazo:</strong> 3-4 semanas
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <h2>Como Funciona</h2>
                <p>O processo é direto. Conversamos sobre o seu negócio e objetivos, eu crio o website, você revisa e dá feedback, fazemos ajustes e lançamos. Simples.</p>

                <p>Depois do lançamento, o website é seu. Não há mensalidades obrigatórias ou taxas escondidas. Se precisar de atualizações ou suporte contínuo, podemos discutir isso separadamente.</p>

                <h2>Exemplos de Trabalho</h2>
                <p>Veja projetos anteriores na <a href="/pt/projetos" class="inline-link">página de projetos</a>. Incluem websites para spas, clínicas dentárias, oficinas e outros negócios locais em Portugal.</p>

                <h2>Tecnologia</h2>
                <p>Construo com ferramentas modernas (Astro, React, Tailwind) que garantem websites rápidos e fáceis de manter. Mas isso é apenas detalhe técnico — o que importa é que funciona bem e é rápido.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="content-sidebar">
                <div class="sidebar-card">
                    <h3>O Que Pode Esperar</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Design limpo e profissional</li>
                        <li>Performance rápida</li>
                        <li>Funciona perfeitamente em mobile</li>
                        <li>Código bem estruturado</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="sidebar-card">
                    <h3>Casos de Uso</h3>
                    <p><strong>Landing Pages:</strong> Campanhas de marketing, promoções, testes de produto, eventos</p>
                    <p><strong>Websites SEO:</strong> Negócios locais, restaurantes, clínicas, serviços profissionais</p>
                </div>

                <div class="sidebar-card cta-card">
                    <h3>Interessado?</h3>
                    <p>Se faz sentido, vamos conversar sobre o seu projeto.</p>
                    <a href="mailto:luismadeira@ruimadeira.pt" class="sidebar-cta">Enviar Email</a>
                    <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/lumadeira" target="_blank" class="sidebar-cta-secondary">LinkedIn</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <script>
        // Mobile Menu Toggle
        const mobileMenuToggle = document.querySelector('.mobile-menu-toggle');
        const navLinks = document.querySelector('.nav-links');

        if (mobileMenuToggle) {
            mobileMenuToggle.addEventListener('click', () => {
                mobileMenuToggle.classList.toggle('active');
                navLinks.classList.toggle('active');
            });

            // Close menu when clicking on a link
            const links = navLinks.querySelectorAll('a');
            links.forEach(link => {
                link.addEventListener('click', () => {
                    mobileMenuToggle.classList.remove('active');
                    navLinks.classList.remove('active');
                });
            });
        }

        // Dropdown navigation
        const dropdownToggle = document.querySelector('.nav-dropdown-toggle');
        const dropdownMenu = document.querySelector('.nav-dropdown-menu');
        const navDropdown = document.querySelector('.nav-dropdown');

        if (dropdownToggle && dropdownMenu) {
            dropdownToggle.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
                e.stopPropagation();
                navDropdown.classList.toggle('active');
            });

            // Close dropdown when clicking outside
            document.addEventListener('click', () => {
                navDropdown.classList.remove('active');
            });

            navDropdown.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
                e.stopPropagation();
            });
        }
    </script>

    <Footer locale="pt" />
</body>
</html>

<style>
/* Reset & Base Styles */
* {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    box-sizing: border-box;
}

:root {
    --color-bg: #0d0d0d;
    --color-text: #c7c7c7;
    --color-accent: #d3e97a;
    --color-dark: #1a1a1a;
    --font-primary: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    --font-heading: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
}

body {
    font-family: var(--font-primary);
    background-color: var(--color-bg);
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: 1.6;
    overflow-x: hidden;
}

/* Navigation */
.navigation {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 24px 60px;
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    background-color: var(--color-bg);
    z-index: 1000;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
}

.logo {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 32px;
    letter-spacing: -0.32px;
    color: var(--color-text);
    text-decoration: none;
}

.nav-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 32px;
    align-items: center;
}

.nav-links a {
    color: var(--color-text);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: -0.48px;
    transition: color 0.3s ease;
}

.nav-links a:hover {
    color: var(--color-accent);
}

/* Dropdown Navigation */
.nav-dropdown {
    position: relative;
}

.nav-dropdown-toggle {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    background: none;
    border: none;
    color: var(--color-text);
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: -0.48px;
    cursor: pointer;
    padding: 0;
    font-family: var(--font-primary);
    transition: color 0.3s ease;
}

.nav-dropdown-toggle:hover {
    color: var(--color-accent);
}

.nav-dropdown-toggle svg {
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
}

.nav-dropdown.active .nav-dropdown-toggle svg {
    transform: rotate(180deg);
}

.nav-dropdown-menu {
    position: absolute;
    top: calc(100% + 16px);
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    background-color: var(--color-dark);
    border: 1px solid #333;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 8px;
    min-width: 160px;
    opacity: 0;
    visibility: hidden;
    transition: opacity 0.3s ease, visibility 0.3s ease;
    z-index: 1000;
}

.nav-dropdown.active .nav-dropdown-menu {
    opacity: 1;
    visibility: visible;
}

.nav-dropdown-menu a {
    display: block;
    padding: 12px 16px;
    color: var(--color-text);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 15px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    transition: background-color 0.2s ease, color 0.2s ease;
}

.nav-dropdown-menu a:hover {
    background-color: rgba(211, 233, 122, 0.1);
    color: var(--color-accent);
}

.mobile-menu-toggle {
    display: none;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 8px;
    cursor: pointer;
}

.mobile-menu-toggle span {
    width: 32px;
    height: 2px;
    background-color: var(--color-text);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
}

/* Page Hero */
.page-hero {
    padding: 120px 108px 80px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #333;
}

.page-hero-content {
    max-width: 900px;
}

.page-hero h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 76px;
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.76px;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
}

.page-hero-subtitle {
    font-size: 24px;
    line-height: 1.4;
    color: var(--color-text);
    opacity: 0.9;
}

/* Content Section */
.content-section {
    padding: 80px 108px;
}

.content-wrapper {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;
    gap: 80px;
}

.content-main h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 36px;
    letter-spacing: -0.36px;
    margin-top: 48px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    color: var(--color-text);
}

.content-main h2:first-child {
    margin-top: 0;
}

.content-main p {
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    opacity: 0.95;
}

.inline-link {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-accent);
    transition: opacity 0.2s ease;
}

.inline-link:hover {
    opacity: 0.7;
}

/* Service Options */
.service-options {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 32px;
    margin: 40px 0;
}

.option-card {
    background-color: var(--color-dark);
    border: 1px solid #333;
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 32px;
    position: relative;
}

.option-card.featured {
    border-color: var(--color-accent);
    background-color: rgba(211, 233, 122, 0.03);
}

.featured-badge {
    position: absolute;
    top: -12px;
    right: 24px;
    background-color: var(--color-accent);
    color: var(--color-bg);
    padding: 6px 16px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
}

.option-card h3 {
    font-size: 24px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    color: var(--color-text);
}

.option-card p {
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    opacity: 0.9;
}

.option-card ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 24px 0;
}

.option-card li {
    padding-left: 24px;
    position: relative;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.6;
}

.option-card li::before {
    content: '→';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-weight: 600;
}

.option-timing {
    margin-top: 24px;
    padding-top: 24px;
    border-top: 1px solid #333;
    font-size: 14px;
    opacity: 0.8;
}

/* Sidebar */
.content-sidebar {
    position: sticky;
    top: 96px;
    align-self: start;
}

.sidebar-card {
    background-color: var(--color-dark);
    border: 1px solid #333;
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 32px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
}

.sidebar-card h3 {
    font-size: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    color: var(--color-text);
}

.sidebar-card p {
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    opacity: 0.9;
}

.sidebar-card p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
}

.sidebar-card ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
}

.sidebar-card li {
    padding-left: 24px;
    position: relative;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.6;
}

.sidebar-card li::before {
    content: '✓';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-weight: 600;
}

.cta-card {
    background-color: rgba(211, 233, 122, 0.05);
    border-color: var(--color-accent);
}

.sidebar-cta {
    display: block;
    text-align: center;
    background-color: var(--color-accent);
    color: var(--color-bg);
    padding: 14px 28px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 15px;
    transition: transform 0.2s ease, background-color 0.2s ease;
    margin-top: 20px;
}

.sidebar-cta:hover {
    background-color: #c5db6f;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
}

.sidebar-cta-secondary {
    display: block;
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    padding: 12px 28px;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-accent);
    border-radius: 8px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 15px;
    transition: background-color 0.2s ease;
    margin-top: 12px;
}

.sidebar-cta-secondary:hover {
    background-color: rgba(211, 233, 122, 0.1);
}

/* Responsive Design */
@media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .navigation {
        padding: 24px 32px;
    }

    .page-hero {
        padding: 80px 32px 60px;
    }

    .content-section {
        padding: 60px 32px;
    }

    .content-wrapper {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        gap: 48px;
    }

    .service-options {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .content-sidebar {
        position: static;
    }
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
    .navigation {
        padding: 20px 16px;
    }

    .logo {
        font-size: 28px;
    }

    .nav-links {
        position: fixed;
        top: 76px;
        right: -100%;
        width: 100%;
        height: calc(100vh - 76px);
        background-color: var(--color-bg);
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: flex-start;
        padding: 40px 0;
        transition: right 0.3s ease;
        border-top: 1px solid #333;
    }

    .nav-links.active {
        right: 0;
    }

    .nav-links a {
        font-size: 24px;
    }

    .nav-dropdown-toggle {
        font-size: 24px;
    }

    .nav-dropdown-menu {
        position: static;
        transform: none;
        margin-top: 16px;
        border: none;
        background-color: transparent;
        padding: 0;
    }

    .nav-dropdown.active .nav-dropdown-menu {
        display: block;
    }

    .nav-dropdown-menu:not(.active) {
        display: none;
    }

    .nav-dropdown-menu a {
        font-size: 20px;
        padding: 12px 0;
    }

    .mobile-menu-toggle {
        display: flex;
    }

    .mobile-menu-toggle.active span:first-child {
        transform: rotate(45deg) translate(8px, 8px);
    }

    .mobile-menu-toggle.active span:last-child {
        transform: rotate(-45deg) translate(8px, -8px);
    }

    .page-hero {
        padding: 60px 16px 40px;
    }

    .page-hero h1 {
        font-size: 48px;
    }

    .page-hero-subtitle {
        font-size: 18px;
    }

    .content-section {
        padding: 40px 16px;
    }
}
</style>
